{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd6896100d","title":"林彪关于整顿机关问题给毛主席的报告","origin":"《工作通讯》1964年4月11日第122期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a52da796a5","index":0,"year":1964,"month":2,"day":20,"articleId":"bd6896100d"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bc531dd819","type":"title","text":"林彪关于整顿机关问题给毛主席的报告","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"ce9c5936fc","type":"authors","text":"林彪","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"8e757ff4cd","type":"appellation","text":"主席：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"8a053b8645","type":"paragraph","text":"为把军队建设工作继续向前推进一步，今年除了仍以主要力量抓连队建设外，拟在目前出一段时间整机关。重点是大抓雷厉风行作风，大抓两头，即：上边的东西（直属上级直至毛主席的指示、著作）及时向下传达，加以具体布置；下边的东西很快地反映上来，加以具体解决。方法是树立标兵，让他们单位比学赶帮。暂定在全军推广空军和陆军一个军部、一个师部的机关工作经验。为了保密，只在军队内部宣传（现场参观和讨论研究），不在报纸上公开发表。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"33623ad5f1","type":"paragraph","text":"以上意见已同总参、总政负责同志谈过，他们都同意，并着手准备从二月下旬开始陆续在上述三个单位开现场会议。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"c7ee471484","type":"paragraph","text":"今后每年除仍用大部分时间抓连队外，抽出一两个月时间整机关作风。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"c4a142bd40","type":"paragraph","text":"特此报告，如有指示请告。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"9ce30a8cc3","type":"paragraph","text":"附上：广州军区文件一份","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"011a70017b","type":"paragraph","text":"空军报告一份","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"5a1516b58c","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"6b9820d365","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"},{"id":"9954c981af","type":"paragraph","text":" 林彪一九六四年二月二十日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d"}],"page":{"id":"50e1af7787","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"bd6896100d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}